{# ── 33/17/50 MODEL ── #}
<section class="coal-model">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="coal-model-rubric reveal">The Coalition Model</div>
    <h2 class="coal-model-h reveal">How sovereign organizations <em>coordinate.</em></h2>
    <div class="coal-model-grid reveal">
      <div class="coal-model-col">
        <div class="coal-model-num">33</div>
        <div class="coal-model-pct">% Institutional seats</div>
        <h3>Black-Led Organizations</h3>
        <p>Autonomous Black-led nonprofits, cooperatives, and community institutions. They join the Coalition as <em>equals</em>, not as subsidiaries.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="coal-model-col">
        <div class="coal-model-num">17</div>
        <div class="coal-model-pct">% Individual builders</div>
        <h3>Individual Builders</h3>
        <p>Technologists, educators, researchers, designers, and strategists who contribute their expertise directly to the network's <em>collective capacity</em>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="coal-model-col">
        <div class="coal-model-num">50</div>
        <div class="coal-model-pct">% Reserved seats</div>
        <h3>Partner Institutions</h3>
        <p>Aligned coalitions, partner institutions, and community organizations whose missions <em>reinforce</em> — but do not duplicate — the Coalition's work.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── PRINCIPLES ── #}
<section class="coal-principles">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="coal-principles-h reveal">The Coalition operates on <em>four principles.</em></h2>
    <div class="coal-principles-list reveal">
      <div class="coal-principle">
        <div class="coal-principle-n">I.</div>
        <div class="coal-principle-body">
          <h3>Sovereignty</h3>
          <p>Member organizations remain sovereign. The Enclave coordinates; it does not absorb. Member data, leadership, and futures stay with their organizations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="coal-principle">
        <div class="coal-principle-n">II.</div>
        <div class="coal-principle-body">
          <h3>Open Record</h3>
          <p>Coalition membership is published openly. Conflicts of interest are declared. The founding masthead above expands only by formal application and agreement.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="coal-principle">
        <div class="coal-principle-n">III.</div>
        <div class="coal-principle-body">
          <h3>Coordination, Not Competition</h3>
          <p>If you are doing this work in Liberty City or anywhere in the diaspora, we are not competing with you. We are in coordination — or we should be.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="coal-principle">
        <div class="coal-principle-n">IV.</div>
        <div class="coal-principle-body">
          <h3>Annual Audit</h3>
          <p>The 33/17/50 model is published, audited, and rebalanced every year. Coalition membership is not a permanent seat — it is a renewed commitment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

